// ─── Outreach Intelligence Brief ──────────────────────────────────────────
//
// Nightly corp-dev / M&A intelligence digest + a persona-matched prospect
// shortlist, surfaced in the Founder Hub Outreach Hub. Populated by the
// /api/cron/outreach-intel sub-job (runs after sync-intelligence so the
// NewsArticle table is fresh). One row per UTC day — `briefDate` is the
// idempotency key so a duplicate dispatch upserts rather than duplicates.
//
// `items` is the distilled corp-dev/M&A signal set; `shortlist` is the
// Phase-B persona match (null until that layer runs). The artefacts this
// feeds NEVER reference a prospect's own deal — every case anchor is a
// PUBLIC 143-library case matched by industry (the ego-threat lock made
// structural, not just prompt-level).

model OutreachIntelBrief {
  id           String   @id @default(cuid())
  briefDate    String   @unique // YYYY-MM-DD (UTC) — idempotency key for the nightly cron
